    "rationale": "The FEA modeling framework demonstrates sufficient credibility for the stated COU. Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 factors meet or exceed required levels. The single below-required factor (Test conditions, achieved 1 vs. required 2) is acknowledged; the compression-bending configuration is the primary regulatory submission scenario and the gap is considered acceptable given the overall evidence package. The model ensemble predictions fall within pre-established acceptance bounds for all three QoIs across both laboratories.",
